The end i believe says "hey babs", but it was in a distance and i had to bring the volume up a bit.  They clearly repeated mine and bruce's name.  I'm only 1 minute in to the recording, so i'll post more if i get anything.  I hope this file helps clear up the fact that we are speaking with someone not of our realm.  I don't need verification, but this file is for those who do.
